Author: Kissescoin
Title: ğŸ”ğŸ”¥[ANN]ğŸ”¥â¤ï¸KISSESâ¤ï¸Blockchain-based ecosystem for adult content distributionğŸ”¥ğŸ”
Body: Hi, JanyJeand31! Good question! The crucial benefit that the blockchain adds to our platform is decentralization. From the perspective of content creators - the advantage is in being able to redeem their earnings immediately (without the standard waiting periods) and furthermore without the hefty middleman fees charged by the big names dominating the industry today. This humble difference offered by our platform proves to be a great device for the empowerment of often vulnerable content creators,  From the perspective of the content consumer, the platform offers a tighter level of anonymity than what would be possible through credit card and other fiat mechanisms. Together with our vision to elevate the variety of content and services on our platform we would seek to provide quality material that is accessible via cryptocurrency and all the advantages that the platform presents besides those quoted above.
